Uses of Package
Catalano.Imaging

  • Packages that use Catalano.Imaging 
    Package Description
    Catalano.Imaging
    The Catalano.Imaging contains base class for manipulation of pixels.
    Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent
    The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent namespace contains base classes for share data among the theads.
    Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters running in parallel.
    Catalano.Imaging.Corners
    The Catalano.Imaging.Corners contains Interest point detectors (i.e Harris, Susan and FREAK)
    Catalano.Imaging.Corners.FREAK
    The Catalano.Imaging.Corners.FREAK Fast Retina Keypoint.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic namespace contains collection classes, which provide different artistic filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Thinning
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Thinning namespace contains collection classes, which provide different thinning algorithms.
    Catalano.Imaging.Tools
    The Catalano.Imaging.Tools namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image moments, analysis textures.
